        onSkip: { zh: "概率 = 有利结果 ÷ 总结果。范围 0~1。$P(\\bar{A}) = 1 - P(A)$。", en: "Probability = favorable ÷ total. Range 0-1. $P(\\bar{A}) = 1 - P(A)$." },
