        onSkip: { zh: "向量加法：$\\binom{a_1}{b_1} + \\binom{a_2}{b_2} = \\binom{a_1+a_2}{b_1+b_2}$。几何意义：首尾相连。", en: "Vector addition: $\\binom{a_1}{b_1} + \\binom{a_2}{b_2} = \\binom{a_1+a_2}{b_1+b_2}$. Geometry: tip-to-tail." },
